        en: 'Multicooker + Air Fryer or Thermomix alone: which to choose?',
        de: 'Multikocher + Airfryer oder Thermomix allein: Was waehlen?',
        es: 'Cookeo + Freidora de aire o Thermomix solo: que elegir?',
